Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒到鎮上來走動 有點累了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:55.22,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(130,123)\fs21\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270\fad(495,0)}我沒有見過這麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:55.22,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(79,135)\fs21\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270\fad(495,0)}迷人的先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道這附近有沒有哪家店的茶比較好喝的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 有一家店不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.82,0:16:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 請務必帶我去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:10.74,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(163,82)\fs24\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270}想著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:10.74,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(105,155)\fs24\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270}他是從哪裡來的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬社長 走…吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這身奇怪的打扮是要幹嘛啊…亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:26.72,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(501,99)\fs24\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270}真實身份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:26.72,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(437,160)\fs24\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270}果然是絕不可以洩漏的
